HEADWORD: Unmortise
<hw>Un*mor"tise</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>mortise</ets>.]</ety> <def>To loosen, unfix, or
